==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gleamy
<hw>Gleam"y</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Darting beams of light; casting
light in rays; flashing; coruscating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In brazed arms, that cast a <qex>gleamy</qex> ray,⟦br⟧
Swift through the town the warrior bends his way.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 630 --></p>

